devilspie|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
devilspie: devilspie (A window-matching utility)
devilspie:
devilspie: A window-matching utility, inspired by Sawfish's "Matched Windows"
devilspie: option and the lack such functionality in Metacity. Devil's Pie can
devilspie: be configured to detect windows as they are created, and match the
devilspie: window to a set of rules. If the window matches the rules, it can
devilspie: perform a series of actions on that window. 
devilspie:
devilspie: http://www.burtonini.com/blog/computers/devilspie
devilspie:
